      • processBiomeArray

        void processBiomeArray(org.bukkit.Location origin,
                       byte[] data,
                       int biomeIndex)
        Process the biome array for a chunk (16x256x16).

        This method will not be called if the chunk is missing biome information.

        Parameters:
        origin - - the block with the lowest x, y and z coordinate in the chunk.
        data - - the data array.
        biomeIndex - - the starting index of the biome data (256 bytes in lenght).
